quote: Yeah turns out he kinda sucks but I do love him

OHHHH shit believe it or not this site is somehow at year 3, just like us :) Happy valentines day my love, and I can't wait for you to see what I have for you this time. Don't worry, I kept around the ability to view previous years, BUT I also added the option to have pictures, which will be a lot of fun. Like I said last year, does this really make sense now that we live together? No. Do I enjoy it anyways? Absolutely. This past year has been incredible, and this is my chance to both tell you that and give you a permanent reminder to come back to. I love you so, so, so much, and I hope that is obvious. Anyways, sit back, relax, and enjoy the ride.
